  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is the observation of the course of

        -  the mechanics of the respiratory system

        -  the endexpiratory lung volume

        -  and the inflammatory response in patients undergoing treatment with extracorporeal life
           support (ECLS) due to severe refractory respiratory failure at our department.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
